casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Kevin W. STRUEMPF, Appellant. WD 81703 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: July 16, 2019 Ellen Flottman, Columbia, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Nathan Aquino, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Three: Thomas H. Newton, P.J., Anthony Rex Gabbert, and Edward R. Ardini, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Kevin W. Struempf appeals his conviction by a Cole County jury of two counts of first-degree statutory sodomy for which he was sentenced to two consecutive terms of twenty years' imprisonment. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
